<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="band faq-band" id="faq">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head center rv">
      <span class="eyebrow">FAQ</span>
      <h2 class="display">Good questions, <span class="hl">straight answers.</span></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="faq rv">
      <details class="faq-item" open>
        <summary>What is LasagnaFi?</summary>
        <p>It's a guide to navigate your personal finances. It gives you insights to improve them. Not just a budgeting app or a data simulator.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Does it use AI?</summary>
        <p>Yes. AI generates the insights. But your personal data is <b>never</b> sent to the AI. All data is anonymized and never tied to you. The model sees numbers and patterns, never your name or accounts.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Why is there a paid tier?</summary>
        <p>It costs money to connect accounts through Plaid, generate your actions, and run the AI chat. It also costs money to host the servers and databases. The paid tier covers those costs. Want it free? Self-host the open source version.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
